      "content": "u sure? it feels more like just bad anxiety from the flight... i've had these kinds of chest pains before when i'm stressed. i dont really want to go to an emergency room in a foreign country if i dont have to, it seems like a lot of hassle for just being nervous. u think i should just try some deep breathing and wait it out for an hour or so?",
